{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779176158202,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_00_WcCzE0kFY6FBJ863TG1G4808","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","content":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM_A — \"Dark Tech\"\n\n**Archetype:** Dark Gradient Glow (Linear-inspired)\n**Reference Company:** Linear.app\n**Background Theme:** Dark (#0B0F1A deep navy)\n**Primary Color Interpretation:** Gradient glow (#4A90D9 → #7B61FF → #00D4FF)\n\n---\n\n## Colors\n\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Background | `#0B0F1A` | Main page background |\n| Surface | `rgba(255,255,255,0.05)` | Cards, modals (glass effect) |\n| Surface Hover | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Card hover state |\n| Sidebar | `#080C14` | Navigation sidebar |\n| Sidebar Active | `#4A90D9` gradient | Active nav item |\n| Text Primary | `#EDF2F7` | Headings, body text |\n| Text Secondary | `#A0AEC0` | Meta, labels, descriptions |\n| Text Tertiary | `#718096` | Captions, placeholders |\n| Border | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Card/input borders |\n| Border Focus | `#4A90D9` | Active/focus border |\n| Primary Gradient | `#4A90D9 → #7B61FF` | Buttons, links, accent |\n| Secondary | `#2D3748` | Secondary buttons, badges |\n| Success | `#4ADE80` (neon glow) | Active/available status |\n| Warning | `#FFB74D` (neon glow) | Pending/attention |\n| Error | `#FF4757` (neon glow) | Errors, destructive actions |\n\n### Status Expression\n- **Active/Available**: `#4ADE80` text + `0 0 10px rgba(74,222,128,0.4)` glow\n- **Pending**: `#FFB74D` text + `0 0 10px rgba(255,183,77,0.4)` glow\n- **Error**: `#FF4757` text + `0 0 10px rgba(255,71,87,0.4)` glow\n- **New badge**: Neon pill — gradient bg + glow shadow\n\n---\n\n## Typography\n\n| Token | Size/Weight | Usage |\n|-------|-------------|-------|\n| Family | `Inter, SF Pro, -apple-system` | All text |\n| H1 | 48px / 700 | Hero headings |\n| H2 | 36px / 700 | Page titles |\n| H3 | 24px / 600 | Section headings |\n| H4 | 20px / 600 | Card titles |\n| Body | 16px / 400 | Main content |\n| Small | 14px / 400 | Meta, labels |\n| Caption | 12px / 400 | Fine print, timestamps |\n| Heading Tracking | `-0.02em` | Tight for tech feel |\n\n---\n\n## Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Grid | 8px |\n| Card Padding | 24px |\n| Section Padding | 48px |\n| Card Gap | 16px |\n| Input Height | 44px |\n| Button Height | 44px |\n| Sidebar Width | 240px |\n\n---\n\n## Shadows\n\n| Level | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Card | `0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)` | Cards |\n| Card Hover | `0 0 0 1px rgba(74,144,217,0.3), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)` | Card hover |\n| Button Glow | `0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.4)` | Primary buttons |\n| Dropdown | `0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1), 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)` | Dropdowns/modals |\n\n---\n\n## Borders & Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Border Style | `1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` |\n| Card Radius | `12px` |\n| Button Radius | `10px` |\n| Input Radius | `8px` |\n| Modal Radius | `16px` |\n| Pill Radius | `9999px` (badges) |\n\n---\n\n## Key Components\n\n### Search Bar\n- Height: 52px, full glass background, hero placement\n- Gradient focus ring on focus\n- Location icon prefix\n\n### Property Card\n- Glass surface (`rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`), backdrop-blur\n- Photo: 280×200px, radius 8px top\n- Price: 22px/700, primary gradient text\n- Stats: 14px text-secondary, icons inline\n- Heart: 24px icon top-right, neon fill when active\n\n### Dashboard Stats Card\n- Glass surface, 24px padding\n- Icon: 32px, primary glow\n- Value: 32px/700, text-primary\n- Label: 14px text-secondary\n\n### Sidebar\n- Background: `#080C14`, 240px wide\n- Nav items: 40px height, 12px radius\n- Active: gradient left border 2px + subtle bg highlight\n- Icons: 20px, secondary → primary on active\n\n### Button (Primary)\n- Gradient bg (`#4A90D9 → #7B61FF`), 44px height\n- Text: white/600, 10px radius\n- Hover: glow intensifies, slight scale\n\n### Button (Secondary)\n- Transparent + border, 44px height\n- Text: text-secondary → text-primary on hover\n\n### Input\n- Glass bg, 44px height, 8px radius\n- Border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- Focus: border-primary + glow outer\n\n### Table\n- Header: text-secondary/12px/uppercase/tracking-wide\n- Row: 48px height, border-bottom rgba(255,255,255,0.04)\n- Row hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\n- Actions: icon buttons 32px\n\n---\n\n## Design Rules\n1. **Dark-first**: all surfaces have dark bg, white text — never white cards on dark\n2. **Glass not solid**: use backdrop-blur + semi-transparent surfaces\n3. **Glow accents**: primary actions get glow shadows, not flat fills\n4. **Tight tracking**: headings use -0.02em for tech precision feel\n5. **Gradient for hierarchy**: primary CTA = gradient, secondary = flat\n6. **Neon status**: status indicators use colored glow, not flat badges\n7. **Monospace for data**: use tabular-nums for prices, stats, tables\n8. **Large photo ratio**: property photos at 4:3, edge-to-edge in cards\n9. **Minimum 8px hits**: all interactive elements ≥ 44px\n10. **Consistent glass**: cards, inputs, modals all use same glass pattern\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","time":{"start":1779176157903,"end":1779176158200}},"id":"prt_e3f28b7ea001hOB7XfcEMsw5O8","sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","messageID":"msg_e3f28a4e2001rLDRpCm2H1YKfv"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779176224320,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01_6GAntTlklLyfJ4c8A42E9279","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","content":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM_B — \"Warm Homely\"\n\n**Archetype:** Warm Cream + Pastel Accents (Notion-inspired)\n**Reference Company:** Notion, Airbnb\n**Background Theme:** Warm Cream (#FFFBF5)\n**Primary Color Interpretation:** Solid primary + warm accent palette (coral, terracotta, sage, amber)\n\n---\n\n## Colors\n\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Background | `#FFFBF5` | Main page background |\n| Surface | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, modals |\n| Sidebar | `#1A1625` (warm dark purple) | Navigation sidebar |\n| Sidebar Active | `#F4A261` warm accent | Active nav item |\n| Text Primary | `#1A1625` | Headings |\n| Text Secondary | `#6B5E53` | Body, descriptions |\n| Text Tertiary | `#A89888` | Captions, placeholders |\n| Border | `#F0E7DB` | Card/input borders |\n| Border Focus | `#E76F51` | Active/focus border |\n| Primary | `#E76F51` (terracotta) | Primary buttons, links |\n| Primary Hover | `#D45D3E` | Button hover |\n| Accent Coral | `#F4A261` | Highlights, badges |\n| Accent Sage | `#2A9D8F` | Success/available indicators |\n| Accent Amber | `#E9C46A` | Warnings, pending |\n| Accent Lavender | `#9B5DE5` | Secondary accent |\n| Surface Warm | `#FFF7ED` | Card variant, callouts |\n| Surface Cool | `#F0F9FF` | Info panels |\n\n### Status Expression\n- **Available**: `#F0FDF4` bg + `#2A9D8F` text (pastel pill)\n- **Pending**: `#FFF7ED` bg + `#E76F51` text (pastel pill)\n- **Sold/Archived**: `#FEF2F2` bg + `#DC2626` text (pastel pill)\n- **New badge**: `#E76F51` bg + white text, rounded-full pill\n\n---\n\n## Typography\n\n| Token | Size/Weight | Usage |\n|-------|-------------|-------|\n| Family | `Plus Jakarta Sans, Inter, -apple-system` | All text |\n| H1 | 48px / 600 | Hero headings |\n| H2 | 36px / 600 | Page titles |\n| H3 | 24px / 500 | Section headings |\n| H4 | 20px / 500 | Card titles |\n| Body | 16px / 400 | Main content |\n| Small | 14px / 400 | Meta, labels |\n| Caption | 12px / 400 | Fine print, timestamps |\n| Heading Tracking | `normal` | Friendly, open |\n\n---\n\n## Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Grid | 4px |\n| Card Padding | 24px |\n| Section Padding | 64px |\n| Card Gap | 20px |\n| Input Height | 48px |\n| Button Height | 48px (pill: 44px) |\n| Sidebar Width | 260px |\n\n---\n\n## Shadows\n\n| Level | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Card | `0 2px 8px rgba(26,22,37,0.04), 0 1px 2px rgba(26,22,37,0.06)` | Cards |\n| Card Hover | `0 4px 16px rgba(26,22,37,0.08), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,22,37,0.04)` | Card hover + lift |\n| Button | `0 2px 4px rgba(231,111,81,0.2)` | Primary buttons |\n| Dropdown | `0 8px 32px rgba(26,22,37,0.1)` | Dropdowns/modals |\n| Soft Lift | `0 1px 3px rgba(26,22,37,0.05)` | Subtle elevation |\n\n---\n\n## Borders & Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Border Style | `1px solid #F0E7DB` |\n| Card Radius | `20px` |\n| Button Radius | `9999px` (pill) |\n| Input Radius | `12px` |\n| Modal Radius | `24px` |\n| Badge Radius | `9999px` (pill) |\n\n---\n\n## Key Components\n\n### Search Bar\n- Height: 56px, white bg, warm shadow, 9999px pill radius\n- Location icon: terracotta color prefix\n- Subtle warm border `#F0E7DB`\n- Hero: centered, large, with decorative warm gradient halo behind\n\n### Property Card\n- White surface with warm soft shadow\n- Photo: 280×210px, radius 20px top\n- Price: 20px/600, terracotta primary\n- Stats: 14px text-secondary, icon + value inline\n- Heart: terracotta fill when active, subtle scale animation\n- \"1 Month Free\" badge: sage pill, pastel bg\n\n### Dashboard Stats Card\n- White surface, 24px padding, warm shadow\n- Icon: 36px in accent color circle (48px)\n- Value: 32px/600, text-primary\n- Label: 14px text-secondary\n- Trend: small up/down arrow in sage/coral\n\n### Sidebar\n- Background: `#1A1625` warm dark purple, 260px wide\n- Nav items: 44px height, 16px radius\n- Active: coral left accent + subtle bg\n- Icons: 20px, coral-tinted on active\n- Logo: warm gradient terracotta → coral\n\n### Button (Primary)\n- Terracotta solid bg, 48px height, 9999px pill\n- Text: white/600\n- Hover: `#D45D3E`, lift shadow intensifies\n\n### Button (Secondary)\n- White bg + warm border, 48px pill\n- Text: text-primary\n- Hover: warm bg `#FFF7ED`\n\n### Button (Ghost)\n- No bg/border, text: primary\n- Hover: warm bg `#FFF7ED`, 12px radius\n\n### Input\n- White bg, 48px height, 12px radius\n- Border: `#F0E7DB`\n- Focus: border-terracotta + subtle warm ring\n\n### Table\n- Header: text-secondary/12px/uppercase\n- Row: 52px height, alternating warm bg stripes\n- Row hover: `#FFF7ED`\n- Actions: icon buttons 36px, terracotta on hover\n\n---\n\n## Design Rules\n1. **Warm first**: cream bg, warm tones — never cold grays\n2. **Soft depth**: shadows are warm-toned, not black — feel gentle\n3. **Pill everything**: buttons, badges, chips all use rounded-full\n4. **Accent palette**: 4 distinct accent colors (coral, sage, amber, lavender) for variety\n5. **Generous whitespace**: section padding 64px+, breathing room\n6. **Pastel status**: statuses use pastel bg + saturated text pills\n7. **Friendly type**: Plus Jakarta Sans, 500-600 weight range, open tracking\n8. **Photo warmth**: property photos get subtle warm overlay gradient\n9. **Large tap targets**: minimum 48px interactive height\n10. **Decorative warmth**: subtle warm gradient halos behind hero/featured sections\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","time":{"start":1779176224004,"end":1779176224317}},"id":"prt_e3f29b44f001QA30F0yEZQl4VX","sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","messageID":"msg_e3f28a4e2001rLDRpCm2H1YKfv"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779176292000,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_02_zOAkEmEzM8P1v2kLlxei1085","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md","content":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM_C — \"Clean Editorial\"\n\n**Archetype:** Pure White Minimal (Apple-inspired)\n**Reference Company:** Apple.com, Stripe\n**Background Theme:** Pure White (#FFFFFF)\n**Primary Color Interpretation:** Sparse accent — primary used ONLY for CTA/active; 95% grayscale otherwise\n\n---\n\n## Colors\n\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Background | `#FFFFFF` | Main page background |\n| Surface | `#FFFFFF` | Cards (identical to bg) |\n| Surface Alt | `#FAFAFA` | Subtle card variant |\n| Sidebar | `#F8FAFC` (light gray) | Navigation sidebar |\n| Sidebar Active | `#FAFAFA` with 3px left `#4A90D9` border | Active nav item |\n| Text Primary | `#1A1A1A` | Headings |\n| Text Secondary | `#6B7280` | Body, descriptions |\n| Text Tertiary | `#9CA3AF` | Captions, placeholders |\n| Border | `0.5px solid #F3F4F6` | Card/input borders (hairline) |\n| Border Focus | `#4A90D9` | Active/focus border |\n| Primary | `#4A90D9` | CTA buttons, active states, links ONLY |\n| Primary Hover | `#3A7BC8` | Button hover |\n| Secondary | `#F3F4F6` | Secondary buttons |\n| Secondary Hover | `#E5E7EB` | Secondary hover |\n| Success | `#059669` | Available/completed |\n| Warning | `#D97706` | Pending/attention |\n| Error | `#DC2626` | Errors, destructive |\n\n### Status Expression\n- **Available**: 6px `#059669` dot only, no text label (or minimal)\n- **Pending**: 6px `#D97706` dot only\n- **Archived/Error**: 6px `#DC2626` dot only\n- **New badge**: `#4A90D9` text only (no bg), uppercase/600/11px tracking-wide\n- **Bold approach**: status is communicated through typography + dots, never pills\n\n---\n\n## Typography\n\n| Token | Size/Weight | Usage |\n|-------|-------------|-------|\n| Family | `SF Pro Display, Inter, -apple-system` | All text |\n| H1 | 64px / 300 (light) | Hero headings — editorial scale |\n| H2 | 48px / 400 | Page titles |\n| H3 | 28px / 400 | Section headings |\n| H4 | 20px / 500 | Card titles |\n| Body | 17px / 400 | Main content |\n| Small | 15px / 400 | Meta, labels |\n| Caption | 13px / 400 | Fine print, timestamps |\n| Heading Tracking | `-0.03em` (H1), `-0.02em` (H2) | Editorial precision |\n| Body Line Height | 1.6 | Generous reading rhythm |\n\n---\n\n## Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Grid | 4px |\n| Card Padding | 32px |\n| Section Padding | 80px (vertical) |\n| Card Gap | 24px |\n| Input Height | 48px |\n| Button Height | 48px (CTA), 40px (secondary) |\n| Sidebar Width | 220px |\n| Max Content Width | 1200px (centered) |\n\n---\n\n## Shadows\n\n| Level | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Card | `none` | Cards — border-only definition |\n| Card Hover | `0 0 0 1px #E5E7EB` | Subtle border emphasis only |\n| Button | `none` | Buttons — no shadow |\n| Dropdown | `0 0 0 1px #F3F4F6, 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` | Dropdowns only |\n| NONE | `none` | Editorial rule: NO shadows anywhere else |\n\n---\n\n## Borders & Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Border Style | `0.5px solid #F3F4F6` (hairline) |\n| Card Radius | `6px` |\n| Button Radius | `6px` |\n| Input Radius | `6px` |\n| Modal Radius | `8px` |\n| Badge Radius | `4px` |\n\n---\n\n## Key Components\n\n### Search Bar\n- Height: 56px, white bg, hairline border\n- Minimal design: no decoration, just input + icon\n- Placeholder: \"Search by city, neighborhood, or ZIP...\"\n- Hero: large, centered, floating over pure white\n- Focus: 1px primary border, no glow\n\n### Property Card\n- White surface, hairline border only (no shadow)\n- Photo: 320×240px, edge-to-edge, radius 0 (square top)\n- Price: 24px/500, text-primary\n- Stats: 15px text-secondary, minimal spacing\n- Heart: 20px icon, subtle fill animation, no color change\n- New badge: `NEW` text label, primary color, uppercase/tracking-wide\n\n### Dashboard Stats Card\n- White surface, 32px padding, hairline border\n- No icon — just value + label\n- Value: 40px/300 light, text-primary\n- Label: 13px text-tertiary, uppercase tracking\n- Border between cards only, no bg differentiation\n\n### Sidebar\n- Background: `#F8FAFC`, 220px wide\n- Nav items: 40px height, 6px radius\n- Active: `#FAFAFA` bg + 3px left primary border\n- Icons: 18px, gray → primary on active\n- Minimal separator lines\n\n### Button (Primary)\n- Primary blue solid, 48px height, 6px radius\n- Text: white/500, SF Pro\n- Hover: `#3A7BC8`, no shadow change\n- Used SPARINGLY — max 1-2 per page\n\n### Button (Secondary)\n- `#F3F4F6` bg, 40px height, 6px radius\n- Text: text-secondary\n- Hover: `#E5E7EB`\n\n### Button (Ghost/Text)\n- No bg, no border, primary text\n- Hover: underline only\n\n### Input\n- White bg, 48px height, 6px radius\n- Hairline border\n- Focus: primary border 1px\n\n### Table\n- Header: text-tertiary/11px/uppercase/tracking-widest\n- Row: 48px height, hairline bottom border only\n- No alternating stripes\n- No row hover bg change (subtle primary text color shift only)\n- Actions: text links only (no icon buttons)\n\n---\n\n## Design Rules\n1. **Typography first**: content hierarchy through type scale, weight, color — not decoration\n2. **No shadows, ever**: cards defined by 0.5px borders only\n3. **Sparse accent**: primary blue ONLY on CTAs, links, active states — never decorative\n4. **95% grayscale**: body is grayscale; color is reserved for action/status\n5. **Generous whitespace**: 80px+ section padding, 1.6 line-height body\n6. **Dot-only status**: status communicated via 6px colored dots + text weight, no pills\n7. **Light type**: H1 at 300 weight, 64px — editorial scale\n8. **Tight radius**: 6px max, square edges preferred\n9. **Minimal chrome**: remove borders, dividers, backgrounds wherever possible\n10. **One CTA rule**: max one primary button visible per viewport section\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md","time":{"start":1779176291540,"end":1779176291997}},"id":"prt_e3f2ab69b001TvGSWV2RIU2loa","sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","messageID":"msg_e3f28a4e2001rLDRpCm2H1YKfv"}}
