>&#10003;</span> Swimming Pool</div>\n          <div class=\"amenity\"><span class=\"check\">&#10003;</span> Air Conditioning</div>\n          <div class=\"amenity\"><span class=\"check\">&#10003;</span> Pet Friendly</div>\n          <div class=\"amenity\"><span class=\"check\">&#10003;</span> Rooftop Deck</div>\n          <div class=\"amenity\"><span class=\"check\">&#10003;</span> Concierge</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section-block\">\n        <h3>Property Details</h3>\n        <table style=\"width:100%\">\n          <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #F0E7DB\"><td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#A89888;width:140px;font-size:13px\">Property Type</td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:500\">Apartment</td></tr>\n          <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #F0E7DB\"><td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#A89888;font-size:13px\">Year Built</td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:500\">2020</td></tr>\n          <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #F0E7DB\"><td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#A89888;font-size:13px\">Floor</td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:500\">3rd</td></tr>\n          <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #F0E7DB\"><td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#A89888;font-size:13px\">Parking</td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:500\">1 assigned spot</td></tr>\n          <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #F0E7DB\"><td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#A89888;font-size:13px\">Pet Policy</td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:500\">Cats &amp; dogs OK ($50/mo)</td></tr>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"section-block\">\n        <h3>Location</h3>\n        <div class=\"map-placeholder\">📍 Google Maps — 123 Main St, Austin, TX 78701</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <aside>\n      <div class=\"inquiry-card\">\n        <h3>Interested in this property?</h3>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">Send an inquiry and the property manager 