{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779177610308,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01_6FzqoKI2nzYSCPmkaZgf4825","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# VARIATIONS_INDEX — NestFind Design Phase\n\nphase: design-variations\ngenerated: 2026-05-19\nvariations_generated: 3\nhtml_files: 9\ntotal_output_files: 13\npages_per_variant: 3\n\narchetypes:\n  - archetype_A: \"Dark Tech (Linear-inspired) — Dark gradient background, glass surfaces, neon glow accents, gradient buttons\"\n  - archetype_B: \"Warm Homely (Notion-inspired) — Cream background, soft warm shadows, pill buttons, pastel status badges\"\n  - archetype_C: \"Clean Editorial (Apple-inspired) — Pure white background, no shadows, hairline borders, light typography, dot-only status\"\n\nreference_companies:\n  - A: Linear.app\n  - B: Notion / Airbnb\n  - C: Apple.com / Stripe\n\ndifferentiation_score: 7/7\n\n---\n\n## Differentiation Checklist\n\n| # | Design Axis | A (Dark Tech) | B (Warm Homely) | C (Editorial) | Different? |\n|---|------------|---------------|-----------------|---------------|-----------|\n| 1 | Background color theme | #0B0F1A dark navy | #FFFBF5 warm cream | #FFFFFF pure white | Yes |\n| 2 | Shadow style | Glow (0 0 20px with primary color) | Soft warm (rgba dark, 0.04-0.08) | None (no shadows anywhere) | Yes |\n| 3 | Border treatment | Transparent rgba(255,255,255,0.08) | Warm tone #F0E7DB solid | Hairline 0.5px #F3F4F6 | Yes |\n| 4 | Corner radius | 12-16px (rounded-xl) | 16-20px + pill (rounded-2xl/full) | 0-6px max (rounded-md) | Yes |\n| 5 | Typography weight | 600-700 bold, tight tracking | 500-600 semibold, open tracking | 300-400 light, editorial scale | Yes |\n| 6 | Status color expression | Neon glow badges (colored glow shadow) | Pastel pills (colored bg + saturated text) | Dot-only + text weight (6px dot) | Yes |\n| 7 | Sidebar theme | Pure dark #080C14 + gradient accent | Warm dark purple #1A1625 + coral accent | Light #F8FAFC + 3px primary left border | Yes |\n\n**Result: 7/7 differentiation — PASS**\n\n---\n\n## File Manifest\n\n### Design Systems (3 files)\n| File | Archetype | Background | Reference |\n|------|-----------|------------|-----------|\n| `DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md` | Dark Tech | #0B0F1A dark | Linear.app |\n| `DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md` | Warm Homely | #FFFBF5 cream | Notion |\n| `DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md` | Clean Editorial | #FFFFFF white | Apple/Stripe |\n\n### HTML Preview Files (9 files)\n| File | Page Type | Archetype | Key Features |\n|------|-----------|-----------|-------------|\n| `A-01-landing.html` | Landing | Dark Tech | Gradient hero, glass cards, neon badges, glow CTA |\n| `A-02-dashboard.html` | Dashboard | Dark Tech | Dark glass sidebar, neon stats, glow status badges |\n| `A-03-detail.html` | Property Detail | Dark Tech | Glass gallery, gradient price, glow inquiry form |\n| `B-01-landing.html` | Landing | Warm Homely | Cream bg, pill search, soft shadows, coral accents |\n| `B-02-dashboard.html` | Dashboard | Warm Homely | Purple sidebar, pastel stat cards, pill statuses |\n| `B-03-detail.html` | Property Detail | Warm Homely | Rounded gallery, warm stats bar, pastel amenity cards |\n| `C-01-landing.html` | Landing | Clean Editorial | Pure white, 64px light hero, hairline borders, minimal cards |\n| `C-02-dashboard.html` | Dashboard | Clean Editorial | Light sidebar, lightweight stats, dot-only status |\n| `C-03-detail.html` | Property Detail | Clean Editorial | Minimal gallery, editorial type, sparse CTA |\n\n### Showcase (1 file)\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `showcase-ALL.html` | Side-by-side iframe grid of all 9 variants |\n\n---\n\n## Structural Markers Verification\n\n| Requirement | Status |\n|-------------|--------|\n| All 9 HTML files have `max-width: 1440px` on root wrapper | PASS |\n| All 9 HTML files have `class=\"var-nav-bar\"` navigation | PASS |\n| `showcase-ALL.html` exists and embeds all 9 variants | PASS |\n| 3 DESIGN_SYSTEM files written | PASS |\n| `VARIATIONS_INDEX.md` exists | PASS |\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\nAfter stakeholder review of these 9 previews:\n1. Select the winning archetype (A, B, or C)\n2. Proceed to Phase 3d: Generate remaining page designs in chosen style\n3. Proceed to Phase 3e: Convert final designs to production React components\n\n---\n\n*Generated by Phase 3a-3c pipeline | 2026-05-19*\n","filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/VARIATIONS_INDEX.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/VARIATIONS_INDEX.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/VARIATIONS_INDEX.md","time":{"start":1779177610001,"end":1779177610306}},"id":"prt_e3f3f414a001v1cS4j3o4SJ1mY","sessionID":"ses_1c0d85630ffesWmsWYPuQ3Gl5W","messageID":"msg_e3f3e3b4a001VRQkpUAkueigmM"}}
